00:39:57,469 --> 00:39:59,136
"to be interfering
with your life.

668
00:39:59,171 --> 00:40:02,206
You seem healthy, with
tremendous physical endurance."

669
00:40:04,676 --> 00:40:07,478
"Bheadr."

