00:41:37,702 --> 00:41:39,102
What about her?

694
00:41:39,137 --> 00:41:40,137
Well, I don't know,

695
00:41:40,171 --> 00:41:44,975
but I saw something
really strange.

696
00:41:45,009 --> 00:41:48,545
- Like what?
- Like, I...

697
00:41:48,580 --> 00:41:51,448
Think she's, like,
a mutant or something,

698
00:41:51,483 --> 00:41:54,284
some kind of, like,
mermaid thing... I...

699
00:41:54,319 --> 00:41:55,952
ugh.

